data.description: This well-kept, 4 BDRM, 2.5 BATH, 2-Story home features laminate wood flooring in the foyer/hallway, formal dining room, kitchen and breakfast area. The carpeted living room includes a wall-mounted 55" TV while the kitchen has granite counters, stainless appliances (no Fridge) and walk-in pantry. Guest Bedroom on main level includes full bath with tile floor and make-up station. The large Primary Suite features a spacious sitting area and bath with dual vanity sinks, garden tub, glass shower and walk-in closet room. Guest beds on upper level share a tiled full bath with dual sinks. Roomy Bonus/Loft for media/office/flex use. Large, level backyard and 10' x 10' patio are enclosed by 6' fence. Chair rail, wainscoting trim, partially finished 2-car garage, water purification system (2019) and MORE!
